LeetCode 1 — Palindrome Number

palindrome_number.py

class Solution:

    def isPalindrome(self, x):

        original = str(x)

        reversed_num = original[::-1]

        return original == reversed_num


obj = Solution()

print(obj.isPalindrome(121))

Output:

True


