LeetCode 2 — Missing Number

missing_number.py

class Solution:

    def missingNumber(self, nums):

        n = len(nums)

        expected = n * (n + 1) // 2

        actual = sum(nums)

        return expected - actual


obj = Solution()

print(obj.missingNumber([3,0,1]))

Output:

2


